 Patients with Hip Fracture are exposed for two traumas that can trigger a stress response.

 The first is the fall that causes the Fracture.

 The second is the surgery.

 In this study the intervention is dispensed early in the disease course - as soon as the Fracture has been diagnosed and booked for surgery.

